import axios from'axios';import FormData from'form-data';import*as actionTypes from'./actionTypes';export var physicianListSuccess=function physicianListSuccess(physicianList){return{type:actionTypes.PHYSICIANLIST_SUCCESS,physicianList:physicianList};};export var selectPhysician=function selectPhysician(phyid,clinicid){return{type:actionTypes.SET_SELECTED_PHY_ID,phyid:phyid,clinicid:clinicid};};export var getPhysicianList=function getPhysicianList(phyname,phycity,physpecialisation){return function(dispatch){var physicianData=new FormData();// Extract the default city from user location, until user search base on location
